      <title>代码截图插件</title>
      <link href="/2020/02/10/202010232031-md/"/>
      <url>/2020/02/10/202010232031-md/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中"><a href="#在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中" class="headerlink" title="在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中"></a>在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中</h2><h3 id="未知大小的元素在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中"><a href="#未知大小的元素在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中" class="headerlink" title="未知大小的元素在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中"></a>未知大小的元素在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中</h3><ol><li>使用弹性盒模型</li></ol><pre class=" language-css"><code class="language-css"><span class="token selector">html,body </span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>  <span class="token property">height</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">100%</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token selector">body </span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>  <span class="token property">display</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> flex<span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token property">justify-content</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> center<span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token property">align-items</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> center<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><ol start="2"><li>使用绝对定位</li></ol><pre class=" language-css"><code class="language-css"><span class="token selector">元素 </span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>  <span class="token property">position</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> fixed<span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token property">top</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token property">bottom</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token property">left</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token property">right</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token property">margin</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> auto<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><ol start="3"><li>使用定位 + 位移（translate）</li></ol><pre><code>元素{    position: fixed;    top: 50%;    left: 50%;    transform : translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%);}</code></pre><h3 id="已知大小的元素在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中"><a href="#已知大小的元素在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中" class="headerlink" title="已知大小的元素在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中"></a>已知大小的元素在屏幕窗口中垂直水平居中</h3><ol><li>使用定位</li></ol><pre class=" language-css"><code class="language-css"><span class="token selector">元素 </span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>  <span class="token property">position</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> fixed<span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token property">top</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">50%</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token property">left</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">50%</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token property">margin-top</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> -元素宽度/<span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token property">margin-left</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> -元素高度/<span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><h2 id="子元素在父元素中垂直水平居中"><a href="#子元素在父元素中垂直水平居中" class="headerlink" title="子元素在父元素中垂直水平居中"></a>子元素在父元素中垂直水平居中</h2><h3 id="未知大小"><a href="#未知大小" class="headerlink" title="未知大小"></a>未知大小</h3><p>1.</p><h3 id="已知大小"><a href="#已知大小" class="headerlink" title="已知大小"></a>已知大小</h3>]]></content>
      
      
